videos.description: Ohio State QB Dwayne Haskins tosses a 48-yard pass downfield to WR Austin Mack, who makes a diving catch at the 2-yard line.
videos.headline: Mack makes unbelievable diving grab

videos.description: Nick Bosa forces a sack fumble on TCU QB Shawn Robinson and Davon Hamilton recovers the loose ball in the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Bosa forces fumble, Buckeyes recover for TD

videos.description: TCU RB Sewo Olonilua takes the handoff and dives across the goal line for the touchdown to put the Horned Frogs on the board.
videos.headline: Olonilua dives across the goal line for TD

videos.description: TCU RB Darius Anderson finds the hole and bursts 93 yards down the sideline for the score.
videos.headline: Anderson flies down sidelines for 93-yard TD

videos.description: Darius Anderson's 93-yard touchdown run is the difference for TCU at the half, up 14-13 on Ohio State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (TCU, OSU locked in close contest at half) 2018/9/15 ESHEET SotFull

videos.headline: TCU, OSU locked in close contest at half

videos.description: Nick Bosa attempts to get to the quarterback, but goes down with an lower ab strain. Bosa would end up walking to the locker room.
videos.headline: Bosa exits to locker room with lower ab strain

videos.description: TCU RB Darius Anderson rushes 16 yards and dives to get the ball in front of the pylon for the score before landing out of bounds.
videos.headline: Anderson dives for second TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins tosses a pass to Parris Campbell, who runs 63 yards for a touchdown. The Buckeyes fail at the 2-point conversion to tie the game.
videos.headline: Haskins finds Campbell for 63-yard TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins lobs a 25-yard pass to K.J. Hill, who makes the catch in the end zone as the Buckeyes extend their lead.
videos.headline: Haskins floats TD pass to Hill

videos.description: TCU QB Shawn Robinson tosses a 51-yard pass downfield to WR TreVontae Hights, who makes the catching falling into the end zone.
videos.headline: Robinson drops 51-yard TD pass to Hights

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins calls his own number and rushes 5 yards into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Haskins keeps it himself for TD

videos.description: Acting head coach Ryan Day explains how Ohio State was able to pull away from TCU and how the defense stepped up without Nick Bosa.
videos.headline: Ryan Day says momentum a key factor in OSU's win

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins takes over in the second half for Ohio State, throwing two and running for another in the 40-28 win against TCU.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Haskins, OSU pull away in second half) 2018/9/15 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Haskins, OSU pull away in second half
